Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,There's so much text in today's world, pretty much none of us have enough time to read all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the things we wish we had time to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:16.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So one of the most exciting applications I've seen of large language models is to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:18.66,灰英字,,0,0,0,,to summarize text
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:24.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And this is something that I'm seeing multiple teams build into multiple software applications
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,You can do this in the ChatGPT web interface
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:31.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I do this all the time to summarize articles so I can just kind of read the content of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,many more articles than I previously could
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:37.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And if you want to do this more programmatically, you'll see how to in this lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:43.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So that's let's dig into the code to see how you could use this yourself to summarize text
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So let's start off with the same starter code as you saw before of import openai, load the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:52.62,灰英字,,0,0,0,,API key and here's that get_completion helper function
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:01:00.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use as the running example, the task of summarizing this product review
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:04.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Got this panda plush toy for my daughter's birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and so on and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:13.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,If you're building an e commerce website, and there's just a large volume of reviews
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:18.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,having a tool to summarize the lengthy reviews could give you a way to very quickly glance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:24.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,over more reviews to get a better sense of what all your customers are thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:27.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here's a prompt for generating a summary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:30.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Your task is generate a short summary of a product review from e commerce website, summarize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:36.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,review below, and so on, in at most 30 words
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:42.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And so this is soft and cute panda plush toy loved by daughter, but small for the price
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,arrived early
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty good summary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:49.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And as you saw in the previous video, you can also play with things like controlling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:55.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the character count or the number of sentences to affect the length of this summary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:59.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Now sometimes when creating a summary, if you have a very specific purpose in mind for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:05.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the summary, for example, if you want to give feedback to the shipping department, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:11.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,also modify the prompt to reflect that so that they can generate a summary that is more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:15.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,applicable to one particular group in your business
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:26.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So for example, if I add to give feedback to the shipping department, let's say I change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:35.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,this to start to focus on any aspects that mention shipping and delivery of the product
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:42.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And if I run this, then again, you get a summary, but instead of starting off with soft and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:49.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,cute panda plush toy, it now focuses on the fact that it arrived a day earlier than expected
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:53.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And then it still has, you know, other details
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:59.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Or as another example, if we aren't trying to give feedback to the shipping department
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:09.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,but let's say we want to give feedback to the pricing department
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:15.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the pricing department is responsible for determining the price of the product
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:22.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to tell it to focus on any aspects that are relevant to the price and perceived
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,value
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:31.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Then this generates a different summary that it says
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,maybe the price may be too high for a size
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:38.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Now in the summaries that I've generated for the shipping department or the pricing department
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:44.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,it focuses a bit more on information relevant to those specific departments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:50.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And in fact, feel free to pause the video now and maybe ask it to generate information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:55.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,for the product department responsible for the customer experience of the product or
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:01.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,for something else that you think might be interesting to an e-commerce site
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:07.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But in these summaries, even though it generated the information relevant to shipping, it had
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:12.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,some other information too, which you could decide may or may not be helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:20.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So depending on how you want to summarize it, you can also ask it to extract information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,rather than summarize it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:27.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here's a prompt that says you're tasked to extract relevant information to give feedback
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,to the shipping department
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:35.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And now it just says, product arrived a day earlier than expected without all of the other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:41.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,information, which was also helpful in a general summary, but less specific to the shipping
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:45.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,department if all it wants to know is what happened with the shipping
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:50.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Lastly, let me just share with you a concrete example for how to use this in a workflow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:56.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,to help summarize multiple reviews to make them easier to read
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here are a few reviews
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:03.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,This is kind of long, but here's a second review for a standing lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:04.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,need a lamp on a bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Here's a third review for an electric toothbrush
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,My dental hygienist recommended
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Kind of a long review about the electric toothbrush
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:17.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,This is a review for a blender when it said, so said 17 piece system on seasonal sale and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,so on and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,This is actually a lot of text
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,If you want, feel free to pause the video and read through all this text
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:28.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But what if you want to know what these reviewers wrote without having to stop and read all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,this in detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:41.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to set review_1 to be just the product review that we had up there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:45.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put all of these reviews into a list
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:53.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And now if I implement a for loop over the reviews
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:06:01.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here's my prompt and here I've asked it to summarize it in at most 20 words
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:07.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Then let's have it get the response and print it out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And let's run that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:16.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And it prints out the first review is that PandaToy review, summary review of the lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:21.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,summary review of the toothbrush, and then the blender
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:29.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And so if you have a website where you have hundreds of reviews, you can imagine how you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:35.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,might use this to build a dashboard, to take huge numbers of reviews, generate short summaries
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:40.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,of them so that you or someone else can browse the reviews much more quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:46.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And then if they wish, maybe click in to see the original longer review
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:51.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And this can help you efficiently get a better sense of what all of your customers are thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,All right, so that's it for summarizing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:00.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And I hope that you can picture if you have any applications with many pieces of text
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:05.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,how you can use prompts like these to summarize them to help people quickly get a sense of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:10.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,what's in the text, the many pieces of text, and perhaps optionally dig in more
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,if they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:17.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,In the next video, we'll look at another capability of large language models, which is to make
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,inferences using text
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:24.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,For example, what if you had, again, product reviews, and you wanted to very quickly get
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:29.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,a sense of which product reviews have a positive or a negative sentiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:49.84,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at how to do that in the next video
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.68,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,当今世界有如此多的文字，但我们几乎没有人有足够的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.76,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,来阅读这些文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:16.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，我认为，大语言模型最令人兴奋的应用之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:18.66,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,是用它来对文本进行总结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:24.48,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这也是我看到多个团队在不同软件应用中构建的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.88,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,你可以在ChatGPT网站上这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:31.00,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我经常用这种方式来总结文章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.00,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这样我就可以比以前多读很多文章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:37.88,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,你将在本课程中，学习如何以编程方式来实现这个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:43.52,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，让我们深入研究代码，看看你如何使用它来总结文本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.28,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,让我们从之前的初始代码开始，导入openai，加载
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:52.62,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,API Key，这里是get_completion辅助函数
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:01:00.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我将以“总结此产品评价”的任务作为运行示例
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:04.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我为女儿的生日买了这只熊猫毛绒玩具，女儿非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.32,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,无论去哪儿都要带上它，诸如此类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:13.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,如果你正在建立一个电子商务网站，并且有大量的评论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:18.68,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,有一个工具可以用来总结冗长的评论，给你提供一种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:24.20,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,让你可以浏览更多评论，更好地了解所有客户的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:27.28,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，这里有一个生成摘要的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:30.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,你的任务是对电子商务网站上的产品评论生成一个简短的总结，总结如下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:36.80,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,下面的评论等等，最多只能用30个字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:42.40,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，这个柔软可爱的熊猫毛绒玩具受到女儿的喜爱，但价格有点小贵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.40,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,提前到货
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.40,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.40,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这是个相当好的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:49.76,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,正如你在前面的视频中看到的，你还可以玩一些东西，比如控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:55.72,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,字符数或句子数来影响这个摘要的长度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:59.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,现在，有时在创建一个摘要时，如果你有一个非常具体的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:05.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,例如，你想给运输部门提供反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:11.20,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,你也可以修改提示来突出这点，这样他们就可以生成一个更好的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:15.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,适用于你业务中的一个特定群体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:26.88,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,例如，如果我想要给运输部门反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:35.80,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,那么我会将关注点集中在商品的运输和交付等方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:42.56,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,如果我运行这个指令，那么你会得到一个新的摘要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:49.12,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这次不是以“柔软可爱的熊猫毛绒玩具”开始，而是强调它比预期提前了一天送达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:53.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,然后它仍然有其他细节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:59.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,或者作为另一个例子，如果我们不是想给运输部门提供反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:09.52,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,而是给定价部门提供反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:15.76,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,定价部门负责确定产品的价格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:22.96,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我会告诉它专注于与产品价格和感知价值相关的任何方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.24,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,价值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:31.52,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,那么这将生成一个不同的总结，它说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.48,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,也许这个尺寸的价格可能太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:38.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,现在，在我为运输部门或定价部门生成的摘要中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:44.40,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,它更侧重于与这些特定部门有关的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:50.00,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,事实上，你可以随时暂停视频
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:55.36,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,然后让它为负责产品客户体验的部门提供有关产品的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:01.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,或者为你认为对电子商务站点有趣的其他某些方面提供信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:07.00,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,但在这些摘要中，尽管它生成了与运输有关的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:12.24,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,但也有一些其他信息，你可以决定这些信息是否有帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:20.12,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，根据你想要总结的方式，你也可以要求它提取信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.96,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,而不是对其进行总结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:27.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，这里有一个提示，说你的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.20,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,提取相关的信息来反馈给给运输部门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:35.44,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,现在它只是说，产品比预期早到了一天，没有其他的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:41.24,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这在一般的总结中也是有帮助的，但如果想知道运输方面发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:45.00,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,就不那么具体了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:50.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,最后，让我与你分享一个具体的例子，说明如何在工作流程中使用这个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:56.76,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,来帮助总结多个评论，使其更容易阅读
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，这里有几条评论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:03.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这有点长，但这是对落地灯的第二个评论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:04.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,需要一盏灯放在卧室里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.28,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这是关于电动牙刷的第三条评论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我的牙科保健师推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,关于电动牙刷的评论有点长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:17.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这是关于搅拌机的评论，当时它说是季节性销售的17件套装系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.92,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,诸如此类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.28,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这实际上是很多的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.28,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意，可以随意暂停视频，读完这些文字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:28.48,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,但是，如果你想知道这些评论者写了什么，而不必停下来阅读所有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.48,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这方面的细节呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:41.60,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,所以我要把 review_1 设为我们之前展示的那个产品评论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:45.32,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我将把所有这些评论放到一个列表中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:53.80,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,现在，如果我对这些评论实施一个for循环
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:06:01.24,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这是我的提示，我要求它最多用20个字来总结它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:07.32,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,然后让它得到响应并打印出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.76,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,让我们运行这个程序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:16.36,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,它打印出的第一条评论是熊猫玩具的评论，灯的总结评论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:21.88,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,牙刷的摘要评论，然后是搅拌器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:29.80,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,因此，如果你有一个网站，你有数百条评论，你可以想象你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:35.36,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,使用它来建立一个控制面板，为大量的评论，生成简短的摘要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:40.76,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这样你或其他人就可以更快地浏览这些评论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:46.20,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,然后，如果他们愿意，可以点击查看原始的长篇评论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:51.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,这可以帮助你更高效地了解所有客户的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,好了，总结就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:00.96,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,我希望你能想象一下，如果你有任何有许多文本的应用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:05.68,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,你可以使用这样的提示来总结，帮助人们快速了解文字中的内容和各种文本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:10.24,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,可以选择进一步深入挖掘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.52,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,如果有需要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:17.64,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,在下一个视频中，我们将看到大语言模型的另一个能力，即
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.88,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,推断的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:24.28,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,例如，如果你有一些产品评论数据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:29.68,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,你希望快速了解哪些评论具有积极或消极情感，该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:49.84,蓝中字,,0,0,0,,让我们在下一个视频中看看如何实现这个功能
